<P>JUDITH. A SACRED DRAMA. As it is performed at the THEATRE ROYAL In DRURY-LANE. The MUSIC compo&s;ed by Dr. ARNE.</P>
<P>LONDON: Printed for J. COOTE, in Pater-no&s;ter Row; and T. DAVIES, in Ru&s;&s;el-&s;treet, Covent-Garden. MDCCLXI. [Price One Shilling.]</P>
</DIV1>
